      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1133 - Ali ibn Ja'far asked his brother Imam Musa ibn Jafar Al-Kadhim (as) about a man leading a group in prayer while wearing trousers (sarawil) and a cloak (rida).\nHe (as) replied: \"There is no harm in it”."
